<h2 class="wp-block-heading">What services are included with the DJ for my party?</h2>

<p>When you book DJ Misha for your party, you can expect a top-grade professional sound system to be provided, including a sound check and appropriate volume level set up. </p>

<p>DJ Misha will be performing by playing and mixing music throughout the duration of your event, and he will also be responsible for the setup and breakdown of any equipment needed for the performance. </p>

<p>Usually DJ Misha arrives about one hour before the event to load in equipment, set up the DJ area and perform a sound check to ensure the music sounds perfect for the given environment. </p>

<h2 class="wp-block-heading">What kind of music does DJ play?</h2>

<p>DJ Misha plays a variety of modern dance music that includes top dance hits, modern takes on 80&#8217;s and 90&#8217;s throwbacks, and house music. He also has a curated collection of music under the EDM category, including tech house, electronica, lounge, deep house, and much more. </p>

<p>DJ Misha will ensure that the music played at your event is tailored to your musical vision and the preferences and demographics of your guests.</p>

