<h2 class="wp-block-heading">Can we make a playlist?</h2>

<p>Yes! DJ Misha would love to know what kind of music resonates with you and your guests. With every booking, you&#8217;ll have a chance to have a conversation about music. </p>

<p>If you would like to select a few songs to better demonstrate your preferences, you can make a playlist on <a href="https://Spotify.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow" title="">Spotify</a> and share it with DJ Misha. </p>

<p>Collaborating with clients and curating the music experience is DJ Misha&#8217;s favorite aspect of DJ&#8217;ing.</p>

<h2 class="wp-block-heading">Does the DJ take requests?</h2>

<p>Generally, guests often want to talk to the DJ and see if he will play a specific song. DJ Misha is happy to engage with guests and hear their song request. DJ Misha, of course, will make the final call if a song request fits into the given moments vibe and energy. </p>

<p>Taking requests as a DJ can be quite distracting from the main focus of performing while mixing music, therefore DJ Misha encourages early communication about music preferences.</p>

<h2 class="wp-block-heading">What should I budget for DJ services?</h2>

<p><strong>For private parties, the starting rate for a 4-hour set is $2000.</strong> This rate includes DJ Misha playing music for the duration of the event, providing a top of the line sound system, and set up and breakdown of equipment.</p>

<h2 class="wp-block-heading">Can DJ travel to my destination or city?</h2>

<p>Yes, DJ Misha can travel nationally and internationally to your destination. Travel expenses include travel by air, ground, and meals. Additionally, we&#8217;ll need to arrange a sound system by a local vendor. DJ Misha will handle all the booking for travel so there is no additional work for you.</p>

